description: A Mileage tracker A Mileage tracker for an Android-based phone. Allows importing and exporting of data in various formats, so it is easy to sync with your existing logs. Key features: * Multiple vehicle support * All new charts (thanks to aiCharts) * Customizable fillup fields * Per-vehicle measurement units * All new statistics * Vastly improved CSV importing * Streamlined import and export * Automatic SD card backups * All new vehicle types * Service interval templates
